data.description: This is a great rambler located in Waite Park Neighborhood with many updates and room to make your own. It has 3 bedrooms and 1.75 bathrooms. The basement is fully finished and has a family room, bathroom, laundry room, storage and 2 offices. The roof and siding have been replaced in the last year. The upstairs has 3 bedrooms, full bathroom, formal dining room, living room and breakfast bar. It has a one car garage, wooded/privacy backyard and a great patio for entertaining. Some of the many updates are new siding 2023, new roof 2022, newly sanded hardwood floors 2023 and much more.
